cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the problem of single image de-raining. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new neural network architecture and training procedure, which involves learning from uncertainty measures, indicating that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of prior information and techniques for image enhancement, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of multi-scale processing, which could place it in cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
